entry.def: If you describe something or someone as unfunny, you mean that they do not make you laugh, although this was their intention or purpose.

example.ex: We became increasingly fed up with his increasingly unfunny and unintelligent comments.
example.tran: 我们越来越反感他益发无趣又缺乏见地的言论。
又一对不好笑的喜剧演员
